{
  "type": "doc",
  "content": [
    {
      "type": "blockquote",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "heading",
          "attrs": {
            "id": "问题描述",
            "data-toc-id": "问题描述",
            "level": 2
          },
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "marks": [
                {
                  "type": "bold"
                }
              ],
              "text": "问题描述"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "marks": [
                {
                  "type": "italic"
                }
              ],
              "text": "前两天有一块SATA固态要挂了，需要临时把系统分区克隆至另一硬盘中。原硬盘为双系统，多个分区，仅将Win10分区使用DG对拷至新分区，已提前建立ESP"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "marks": [
                {
                  "type": "italic"
                }
              ],
              "text": "MSR分区，并在对拷后修复了引导。开机后系统正常引导，但卡在了win10加载状态（无限转圈）："
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "orderedList",
          "attrs": {
            "start": 1,
            "type": null
          },
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "listItem",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "鼠标指针"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "marks": [
                        {
                          "type": "bold"
                        }
                      ],
                      "text": "可见可移动"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "；"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "listItem",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "五次shift"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "marks": [
                        {
                          "type": "bold"
                        }
                      ],
                      "text": "可弹出"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "粘滞键提示框"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "image",
                  "attrs": {
                    "src": "https://hry.54120721.xyz/file/Windows/1778432436873_1.jpg",
                    "alt": "出现问题",
                    "title": null,
                    "width": "100%",
                    "height": null,
                    "align": "center",
                    "caption": "",
                    "aspectRatio": null
                  }
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "id": "解决方案",
        "data-toc-id": "解决方案",
        "level": 2
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "bold"
            }
          ],
          "text": "解决方案"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "0x00 : 进入PE，Windows + R 运行 regedit"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "attrs": {
        "src": "https://hry.54120721.xyz/file/Windows/1778432429285_2.jpg",
        "alt": "步骤一",
        "title": null,
        "width": "100%",
        "height": null,
        "align": "center",
        "caption": "",
        "aspectRatio": null
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "0x01 : 单击HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE选中（否则下一步按钮会置灰）"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "attrs": {
        "src": "https://hry.54120721.xyz/file/Windows/1778432433126_3.jpg",
        "alt": "步骤二",
        "title": null,
        "width": "100%",
        "height": null,
        "align": "center",
        "caption": "",
        "aspectRatio": null
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "0x02 : 菜单栏 文件 -> 加载配置单元（HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE需为选中状态）"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "attrs": {
        "src": "https://hry.54120721.xyz/file/Windows/1778432435224_4.jpg",
        "alt": "步骤三",
        "title": null,
        "width": "100%",
        "height": null,
        "align": "center",
        "caption": "",
        "aspectRatio": null
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "0x03 : 进入"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "bold"
            }
          ],
          "text": "系统分区"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "，打开 "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "bold"
            }
          ],
          "text": "Windows\\System32\\config\\SYSTEM"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "文件"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "attrs": {
        "src": "https://hry.54120721.xyz/file/Windows/1778432432100_5.jpg",
        "alt": "步骤四",
        "title": null,
        "width": "100%",
        "height": null,
        "align": "center",
        "caption": "",
        "aspectRatio": null
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "0x04 : 在弹出的对话框中设置一个临时项名称(尽量使用英文且不与内部项名称相同)"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "attrs": {
        "src": "https://hry.54120721.xyz/file/Windows/1778432435445_6.jpg",
        "alt": "步骤五",
        "title": null,
        "width": "100%",
        "height": null,
        "align": "center",
        "caption": "",
        "aspectRatio": null
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "0x05 : 展开刚刚的项名称所在项，单击“"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "bold"
            }
          ],
          "text": "MountedDevices"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "”"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "attrs": {
        "src": "https://hry.54120721.xyz/file/Windows/1778432442534_7.jpg",
        "alt": "步骤六",
        "title": null,
        "width": "100%",
        "height": null,
        "align": "center",
        "caption": "",
        "aspectRatio": null
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "0x06 : 选中MountedDevices，仅删除右侧窗格中的数据值（\\DosDevices\\C:等），不要删除左侧的MountedDevices文件夹"
        },
        {
          "type": "hardBreak"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "注 : 此操作会导致系统重启后重新分配盘符。若原系统有多个分区，盘符可能与原顺序不同（如原D盘变E盘），进桌面后需在\"磁盘管理\"中手动调整。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "attrs": {
        "src": "https://hry.54120721.xyz/file/Windows/1778432439737_8.jpg",
        "alt": "步骤七",
        "title": null,
        "width": "100%",
        "height": null,
        "align": "center",
        "caption": "",
        "aspectRatio": null
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "0x07 : 重新选中刚刚设置的名称，文件 -> "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "bold"
            }
          ],
          "text": "卸载配置单元"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "（未选中则该选项会处于置灰状态）"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "attrs": {
        "src": "https://hry.54120721.xyz/file/Windows/1778432441975_9.jpg",
        "alt": "步骤八",
        "title": null,
        "width": "100%",
        "height": null,
        "align": "center",
        "caption": "",
        "aspectRatio": null
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "attrs": {
        "src": "https://hry.54120721.xyz/file/Windows/1778432434514_10.jpg",
        "alt": "步骤九",
        "title": null,
        "width": "100%",
        "height": null,
        "align": "center",
        "caption": "",
        "aspectRatio": null
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "0x08 : 重启，系统正常进入，修复完成。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "id": "原理简述",
        "data-toc-id": "原理简述",
        "level": 2
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "bold"
            }
          ],
          "text": "原理简述"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "orderedList",
      "attrs": {
        "start": 1,
        "type": null
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "MountedDevices存储了磁盘签名与盘符的绑定关系。"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "硬盘对拷后，新盘的磁盘签名发生变化。"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "但注册表仍指向旧盘，导致系统加载时找不到系统分区而假死。"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "清空后Windows会重新扫描并重建映射。"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph"
    }
  ]
}